Slap down the Creatures. Get Relics into play; Gia&#39;s Tome works especially nice. Zaya&#39;s high energy allows tons of Creatures to be played.<br>
<br>
Yerthe:<br>
<br>
The Hyren Magi. PLays Grass Hyren, whose Effect prevents damage, and with &quot;ENERGIZE: 1&quot;, it&#39;ll almost be unstoppable. One Staff of Hyren in the deck, for Yerthe only.<br>
<br>
Marella:<br>
<br>
Awesome Energize Rate. Nightmare Channel still doesn&#39;t have much affct. The one card restriction isn&#39;t that bad, there are always plenty of cards in my hand at all times for some reason anyway.<br>
Play some really big Creatures with Marella: Junjertrug, etc. </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font face="Haettenschweiler, Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif" size="5" COLOR="#000000"> </Font></TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">DeckTech <BR> For the Players, By the Players  <BR>www.decktech.net </FONT></TD></TR></table> 
